lsy / listsystemcolour        Lists colours of Axmud system messages

   Format:
      ;lsy                    Lists system colours

   Notes:
      Lists the colours of various system messages, as well as the colour used
         to displayed world commands (commands sent to the world).
      Use the ';setsystemcolour' command to modify these colours.

   User commands:
      lsy / listsyscol / listsystemcolor / listsystemcolour
